    "MtVapiusShipping_Objective_0_Text_Translated": "crecer 40{Crop:TextPlural}.",
    "MtVapiusShipping_Objective_1_Text_Translated": "Lugar 40{Crop:TextPlural}en la caja de Mt Vapius Inn.",
